{
  "stem": "7458.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And if he finds out that I am hiding you, he'll kill me, and he'll kill you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But I'm not going to let you die.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I'm going to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] hide you in-- in a barn where there were pigs on the main floor and straw and hay above.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I'm going to hide you there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And when I can, when my husband is not home, and the children are not around, I'll bring you some medicine, some fat for your frozen body, and some food whenever I can.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And she said to me, promise me that [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] every day you'll say, I'll die tomorrow, but not today.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[CRYING] Well, she-- she kept her promise.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "She gave me some food and whatever she could.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And a few weeks later, one night I heard knocking on the door.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And two young men came begging for food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They were two brothers from my hometown, the older one, Chonen, and the younger one Ruvak.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And they-- Ruvak was actually my brother's classmate, and Chonen was one year older than I.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And they came begging for food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And the woman told them that she was hiding me in the barn.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And that night, I joined up with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And they were hiding out in the forest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "It was very difficult to hide in the forest, because there was lots of snow, and it would leave trails.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "So they were hiding in farmers' barns.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They would break a board off and crawl in and hide in the hay during the day and sometimes at night.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And they would go out begging for food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And so I joined them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "By that time, it must have been about March of 1943.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And the weather improved a bit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And I joined Ruvak and Chonen.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
